Barbara Weeks (radio actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Weeks_(radio_actress) 0 Barbara Weeks (October 27, 1906 - July 4, 1954) was an American actress and voice talent in the Golden Age of Radio. She was best known for her work in soap operas. Barbara_Weeks ( October_27_,_1906 - July_4_,_1954 ) was an_American_actress_and_voice_talent in the_Golden_Age of Radio .
